{"tid":1745264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"選管會在選舉後才「可能處理」無此人的種票信件","createTime":"2019-11-22T06:35:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T04:35:23.000Z","uid":15696,"like":323,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":104,"replies":[{"pid":"1029d52c4753a4411056ff51900f8d175f397def","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"話就話唔夠人手，要調查清楚，有高層仲話唔洗處理，話唔排除有人(eg.D仔女)玩嘢喎<br />\n記者快D去信質問吓，睇佢點答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無此人都可以去投票，勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/4hWu1Zh.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張相話你知種票問題幾嚴重<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745176</a>"},{"pid":"e2e348d3073b157db43a4a3ebb97ee50e64e3368","tid":1745264,"uid":187629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0145366404bbe2e94435eef9e8d44f4b91d9ca33","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"記者去問吓就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a36f96f0a7314f828bb9ec5333494fa5135971","tid":1745264,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809f858dc2c10203da0d1372bce704f9ae1bef1f","tid":1745264,"uid":144847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"31237d2ccce11a3e2c21ef1f7d7bd490c62a006c","tid":1745264,"uid":184366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"推到記者見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67327659a16eec79f38da8e5dc639373e08f6f0c","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:39:28.000Z","msg":"有&quot;無此人&quot;信去搵候選人查吓<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />100%肯定登記仲係度"},{"pid":"62a9bb01354038af2522e4498802bd903a0738e3","tid":1745264,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c46f3d4b6396a85a4303d8758a4a3228f27ab3","tid":1745264,"uid":810,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"投左咁多年票 種足咁多年<br />\n香港人都仲係默默地接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b54064625e6b7863d12105c14166600590c8b1c0","tid":1745264,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"Del圖啦屌 睇到邊區呀 做彈信嘅每區來來去去都係嗰幾丁友 又想害到手足冇咗份工"},{"pid":"8612f5ae532fe635fbabe11c31ca05d8a114fb0a","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">市民要留意，如果只向選舉事務處「反映」有問題個案，或未能取消其投票權。</span><br />\n<br />\n98%只將通知書退回選舉事務處<br />\n<br />\n連月來有反修例市民批評政府漠視民意、拒絕回應訴求，又不滿建制派議員在事件中為政府護航，表明要建制派在選舉中「票債票償」。<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉在今年11月底舉行，選舉事務處在8月1日公布2019年臨時選民登記冊，記者向處方了解自8月1日至8月19日，有多少市民曾反映或舉報其住址疑被他人利用作選民登記。選舉事務處回覆指，截至19日中午，共有344宗相關個案，其中有336宗（98%）是巿民收到不屬其本人或同住者的登記通知書，並將通知書退回予處方；其餘8宗個案是市民不滿就有人涉嫌利用他人居住地址登記為選民，而向處方投訴或舉報，其中有一名市民更就其個案提出反對，反對有人以其居住地址登記為選民。"},{"pid":"b5c0869bc285a4d69cee74d94bf88b7967134148","tid":1745264,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"btw 退信冇撚用㗎 拎ID去就投得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7ba115e7d3d5447003c77882ef9ca451215f40","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b5c0869bc285a4d69cee74d94bf88b7967134148","tid":1745264,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"btw 退信冇撚用㗎 拎ID去就投得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:43:50.000Z","msg":"正確 要提出反對先有用"},{"pid":"34bcbceda16ef2c6659482f44cb17f0f7ea90883","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:45:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">取消種票幾撚複雜  </span><br />\n<br />\n選舉事務處表示，現正覆核吳小姐及其餘343宗個案，會與相關申請人聯絡，以核實其登記住址。如申請人未能提供合理解釋，處方會在編製2019年正式選民登記冊時，尋求審裁官批准將其選民登記取消。<br />\n<br />\n同時，處方亦發現部份個案屬於文書錯誤，或選民在登記表上將部份居住地址錯誤填寫，處方會有相應的跟進，尋求審裁官批准更正有關的選民登記資料。就一名市民提出反對有人以其居住地址登記為選民，處方會將該個案呈交審裁官裁決，如審裁官接納，其選民登記將被取消。"},{"pid":"0f592832de2c405a0f6205354b1581e8c6fd93f1","tid":1745264,"uid":31151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:45:57.000Z","msg":"揾候選人/議員 等佢地追啦 我地追得鬼閒采我地咩"},{"pid":"3e56cb72c91d4b667ef995c3ce52cb49f4a1e7fb","tid":1745264,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:48:50.000Z","msg":"得返兩日點處理"},{"pid":"141bfb96f685e3d404b2a1ab1bc7e4e2fb5c082f","tid":1745264,"uid":95577,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b54064625e6b7863d12105c14166600590c8b1c0","tid":1745264,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"Del圖啦屌 睇到邊區呀 做彈信嘅每區來來去去都係嗰幾丁友 又想害到手足冇咗份工"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:48:53.000Z","msg":"都唔會嘅<br />\n你見信面都有人寫無此人<br />\n係市民寫嘅<br />\n唔關職員事"},{"pid":"ad563c0cb375195da751d73cbc2192472e548f3d","tid":1745264,"uid":229607,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"141bfb96f685e3d404b2a1ab1bc7e4e2fb5c082f","tid":1745264,"uid":95577,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b54064625e6b7863d12105c14166600590c8b1c0","tid":1745264,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"cited