d7b04","tid":1745264,"uid":279895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:22:54.000Z","msg":"推畀記者睇"},{"pid":"ca59720a119993cd9243639737e9166bf36ab49e","tid":1745264,"uid":151168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:22:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3c875919290729821dbcf64abcc4c6b288baa3d","tid":1745264,"uid":190579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8612f5ae532fe635fbabe11c31ca05d8a114fb0a","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:41:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">市民要留意，如果只向選舉事務處「反映」有問題個案，或未能取消其投票權。</span><br />\n<br />\n98%只將通知書退回選舉事務處<br />\n<br />\n連月來有反修例市民批評政府漠視民意、拒絕回應訴求，又不滿建制派議員在事件中為政府護航，表明要建制派在選舉中「票債票償」。<br />\n<br />\n區議會選舉在今年11月底舉行，選舉事務處在8月1日公布2019年臨時選民登記冊，記者向處方了解自8月1日至8月19日，有多少市民曾反映或舉報其住址疑被他人利用作選民登記。選舉事務處回覆指，截至19日中午，共有344宗相關個案，其中有336宗（98%）是巿民收到不屬其本人或同住者的登記通知書，並將通知書退回予處方；其餘8宗個案是市民不滿就有人涉嫌利用他人居住地址登記為選民，而向處方投訴或舉報，其中有一名市民更就其個案提出反對，反對有人以其居住地址登記為選民。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<br />\n退咗等於確認<br />\n<br />\n仲要而家先講<br />\n封信就退咗<br />\n冇仇報"},{"pid":"98181644fc0e718dccb0f5e2414a611c8a24ed62","tid":1745264,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"國際戰線<br />\n<br />\n中共打算大規模 選舉舞弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4712e48cc73c58e0f94b6a4f2c0936a96e77bf2","tid":1745264,"uid":95181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:27:47.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"95be558ecb2763dfebbaa4f45f80e1d3f4a4b537","tid":1745264,"uid":46894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"呢D就係真正的選舉不公"},{"pid":"09f2639f443054312c63efc7bd0d152dd9252e2e","tid":1745264,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:28:47.000Z","msg":"推到國際！"},{"pid":"6f1cc88f20f868a41c64d4d5be81f9678c64a6b2","tid":1745264,"uid":165213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:29:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都投撚完啦 屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"90361955f8b94d552f307117fdcae2b44e00b9c6","tid":1745264,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8147425b01b10fc2ace0ac2d2d2cddd24530e461","tid":1745264,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72be3979ed1c16e9b2981d4afcaf29c54717ad8","tid":1745264,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去五個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依五個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來都無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ourtreehole\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fourtreehole&d=eu0lilLN9Tjy39QEn%2BRylgHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=dd2774e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ourtreehole</a><br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，反抗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abf64d575d06b154d5251a2b93aee2c3076b8fb","tid":1745264,"uid":17400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:35:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f417a1dfb7f0e49af58c3ec1c81f782f5f021d9d","tid":1745264,"uid":49359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1029d52c4753a4411056ff51900f8d175f397def","tid":1745264,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"話就話唔夠人手，要調查清楚，有高層仲話唔洗處理，話唔排除有人(eg.D仔女)玩嘢喎<br />\n記者快D去信質問吓，睇佢點答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  無此人都可以去投票，勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/4hWu1Zh.jpg\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張相話你知種票問題幾嚴重<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745176</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:36:38.000Z","msg":"有無人通知所羅門<br />\n做有做定文宣"},{"pid":"113a410fa7d5e7c3cff960de7d9518077110386a","tid":1745264,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"手足開ot做都做唔切"},{"pid":"15c8af0dbaffe5ad6275f536a9680895e828c362","tid":1745264,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1029d52c4753a4411056ff51900f